title: PoI Ladies || S&M || //Person of Interest//
author: KarxDanvers
comment: Oh god. the chemistry between Root & Shaw is just like... WOW.

Finally, a video of this song with the ladies of Person of Interest that actually includes Zoe (especially applauds your use of clips with her to the lyric 'Feels so good being bad, there's no way I'm turning back'

I'll take Shaw anytime, anywhere, my favorite! I'll take her over Reese.
